item.title: CVE-2020-6366|2024-08-04T09:02:39.996Z -- sap%20se -- sap%20netweaver%20%28compare%20systems%29
item.description: SAP NetWeaver (Compare Systems) versions - 7.20, 7.30, 7.40, 7.50, does not sufficiently validate uploaded XML documents. An attacker with administrative privileges can retrieve arbitrary files including files on OS level from the server and/or can execute a denial-of-service.
